{"tid":2233026,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國糧食又出事 2500噸毒鎘米入藏廣東","createTime":"2020-10-06T23:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T02:49:23.000Z","uid":141151,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ceac29da3114950229d67e7dbc7764f3c966e1ff","tid":2233026,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T23:15:32.000Z","msg":"中國糧食又出事 2500噸毒鎘米入藏廣東<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20201006-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B3%A7%E9%A3%9F%E5%8F%88%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%8B-2500%E5%99%B8%E6%AF%92%E9%8E%98%E7%B1%B3%E5%85%A5%E8%97%8F%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20201006-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B3%25A7%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%258F%2588%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25BA%258B-2500%25E5%2599%25B8%25E6%25AF%2592%25E9%258E%2598%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E5%2585%25A5%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmeIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=477a2ce1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20201006-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B3%A7%E9%A3%9F%E5%8F%88%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%8B-2500%E5%99%B8%E6%AF%92%E9%8E%98%E7%B1%B3%E5%85%A5%E8%97%8F%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1</a><br />\n<br />\n中國廣東省陽江國家糧食儲備中轉庫，近日被踢爆混入2500多噸鎘超標稻穀，時間長達2至3年。根據中國法院判決書顯示，共有4人涉案，分別被判處1年至5年徒刑。對此，中國民眾相當不滿，認為處罰根本過輕，到時候保外就醫、獄中表現良好提早出獄，這件事就&ldquo;相忘於江湖&rdquo;。消息沒有提及數千噸鎘超標稻穀的下落。<br />\n<br />\n據聯合新聞網今天報道說，中國糧食頻出事，2500噸毒鎘稻米藏廣東。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國法院判決書顯示，在2017年至2018年期間，4名被告多次購入湖南攸縣的鎘超標稻穀，並將其運送至廣東陽江市東城國家糧食儲備中轉庫。兩年間，被告共向廣東陽江市東城國家糧食儲備中轉庫運送了上萬噸稻穀，其中大約2597噸鎘超標。法院以&ldquo;不符合安全標準的食品罪&rdquo;對4人處以1年至5年徒刑。消息被媒體揭露後，有許多中國網友感嘆&ldquo;處罰輕了吧？&rdquo;、&ldquo;人間地獄，在正常人眼中的重罪基本輕判，輕罪基本重判。&rdquo;、&ldquo;保外就醫，獄內表現良好減刑提前出院，相忘於江湖&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n據該報道，除了鎘超標稻穀，中國今年4月也爆出鎘超標毒大米事件，涉及7家湖南省益陽市的企業。該事件曝光後，已經有大量毒大米製成米腺流向雲南等多地，剩餘的鎘超標毒大米數量大約為99.42噸。根據醫學界專家的警告，長期食用鎘含量高的食物，可能損害腎臟。"},{"pid":"5ef445bcc741383a1eb3630b8b8b5e0cf8e63cfa","tid":2233026,"uid":245409,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T23:17:43.000Z","msg":"跟手又借d易燒糧倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a359eddaec3c5a479b4d113233114445636fee1","tid":2233026,"uid":326287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T23:19:55.000Z","msg":"泰國米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6944d74708b6e0cf66386e8abad2114cfc019c19","tid":2233026,"uid":342828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T23:27:48.000Z","msg":"759前排有款越南米，質素都唔錯。不過最近賣晒又未有新貨到，所以仲等緊。終國人食埋咁多重金屬，就嚟個個都變晒ironman。"},{"pid":"0cabc06fcfbb46ad2541eab030e2e8dc6117f874","tid":2233026,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T23:30:08.000Z","msg":"點解支那咁多黑心食品？"},{"pid":"2cf6a9156e1c429c76838e743461e0c60c358a5e","tid":2233026,"uid":88743,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T23:31:27.000Z","msg":"稀土米<br />\n可以拎黎做龍芯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00086f9358d741aa0ecf1844a1bcc9ef5c80dbf0","tid":2233026,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T23:34:37.000Z","msg":"不滿？食你就食啦冚家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ffbe12ce40043781f54450e8b13aaf6018eff40","tid":2233026,"uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T23:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s1.stickers.cloud/packs/c82596a4-31b4-4a93-a5f0-3a18146f7aa8/webp/b8f1ee88-1d87-4251-86c2-f6f56059142a.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.stickers.cloud%2Fpacks%2Fc82596a4-31b4-4a93-a5f0-3a1